{"tid":252183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那家庭掟麵包糠落海   加拿大海獅被騷擾扯支那女童落海","createTime":"2017-05-21T13:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T16:14:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4289652915b1e821d47a517009d7e076ecb9a2","tid":252183,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170521/large/1495363305_999d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170521%2Flarge%2F1495363305_999d.jpg&h=3e014dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大卑詩省史提夫斯頓港內，西門菲莎大學生Michael Fujiwara目擊事發經過，他在碼頭上到一隻雄性海獅向旅客游戈過來，當時有一個家庭拿麵包糠餵牠，而一名小女孩則接近碼頭邊緣。<br />\n<br />\n「我估計海獅第一次跳起只是試該女孩，之後再次躍起，將女孩拖入中海中。」 Michael Fujiwara表示，一名男子立即跳入海中救女孩，但不知其身份是否與女孩有關。事件中，沒有人受傷，而該家庭立即帶同女孩離開碼頭。他說：「他們一家人看起來很震驚。」Michael Fujiwara又說，他每周都會到碼頭看海獅，但從沒見過影片中海獅發惡的情況。<br />\n<br />\n卑詩省海洋專家認為，餵飼野生動物是愚蠢的行為，「該隻加州海獅屬於雄性，體型龐大的動物，並不是表演動物，未曾在人類身邊訓練過。」專家估計，該女孩背着海獅，海獅可能以為裙子是食物，因而躍出水面覓食，才咬着其裙子拉她下海。根據加拿大海洋動物規例，除了釣魚外，不准騷擾任何海洋生物。<br />\n<br />\nCBC News"},{"pid":"a5aa79b66d0509045fa3f9c37c630083a31bca83","tid":252183,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170521/large/1495362512_cd5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170521%2Flarge%2F1495362512_cd5f.jpg&h=200593c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170521/large/1495362511_6272.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170521%2Flarge%2F1495362511_6272.jpg&h=dfb6addb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大史提夫斯頓港內昨日出現一隻海獅，吸引遊客駐足圍觀，一名說支那蝗語女童坐在岸邊似乎想要與海獅合照，結果海獅突然躍出咬住小女孩，瞬間將她拖入海中，所幸旁人立即跳下海中救援，幸好女童及時獲救，沒有造成傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n網友Michael Fujiwara將這段影片上傳到《YouTube》頻道，影片中，海獅接近時讓遊客們很開心，牠一開始還輕輕躍起嚇了小女孩一跳，想不到原來這第一次只是試探，第二次再躍起時直接把小女孩拖入海中，旁邊一名中年男子立即跳入海中救人，即時將小女孩救起。小女孩獲救後，家人快速將她帶離，邊以支那蝗語說：「不要怕，不要怕」。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube／台灣《蘋果日報》"},{"pid":"e752da9e322e803101d30e87599d39884a9f8ea8","tid":252183,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母個男人多撚事<br />\n<br />\n驚唔驚生仔冇屎忽"},{"pid":"aeed5c922659c3e499dacb86870848f4f607c19c","tid":252183,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌佢老母個男人多撚事<br />\n<br />\n驚唔驚生仔冇屎忽</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d67b511a4098f502940418e9e693f9db8d7d9f","tid":252183,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌佢老母個男人多撚事<br />\n<br />\n驚唔驚生仔冇屎忽</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n隔離post一早有片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個男人都係蝗<br />\n可能仲係個細路女既屋企人"},{"pid":"27b0db57fd741b9c1bb3af7a8dc1d85f81b125d6","tid":252183,"uid":106087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌佢老母個男人多撚事<br />\n<br />\n驚唔驚生仔冇屎忽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解唔係鬧支那人白痴 無啲危機意識<br />\n<br />\n而係怪人地去救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n梳 真心左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc769566cf8a649ea8b2cbe747183ff547ebcd11","tid":252183,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"人地想食魚 你就搵d麵包掟鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88948b33a48b1d29b71c554820a382ae1f76592a","tid":252183,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:34:23.000Z","msg":"張圖諗起啲不定拉上拉落嘅GIF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n恥度極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a551a805e0e3ab31102d25739df64fa8b4bd1d","tid":252183,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張圖諗起啲不<span style=\"color: red;\">停</span>拉上拉落嘅GIF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n恥度極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"daa42fa3179cf170f105631a4fd950c64e9d51ce","tid":252183,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T16:14:46.000Z","msg":"佢外公嚟<br />\nD人無視警告"}]}